{"tid":632413,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"稱供港食品99.999%安全　黨報批「因為港嚴格檢測」說法顛倒邏輯","createTime":"2018-04-17T11:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-18T06:44:36.000Z","uid":53379,"like":2,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"94604ae6d199eee990b335064ad7d178a71ec958","tid":632413,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:04:16.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">稱供港食品99.999%安全　黨報批「因為港嚴格檢測」說法顛倒邏輯</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n古語有云「民以食為天」，食物安全一直備受關注。內地官媒《人民日報》海外版署名文章指，內地供港農產品創造了「近60年保持99.999%安全率的驚人紀錄」，但強調內地供港食品品質高非因香港嚴格檢測，而是「『供給側』的自我要求」。<br />\n<br />\n文章題為＜六十年如一日 高品質不打折 供港蔬菜安全率 「5個9」咋做到的＞，提到本港食環署檢查組近日到廣東清遠供港蔬菜種植基地考察，3家基地都交出了「零不符合項成績單」，形容內地供港農產品「已經創造了近60年保持99.999%安全率的驚人紀錄」、「始終保持黃金品質」。<br />\n<br />\n文章之後表示，有人認為供港食品品質高，原因在港府對食品安全有嚴格標準並實行集中管理，但文章批評這邏輯「有點顛倒」，「因為香港方面的檢測愈嚴，出現不合格狀況的可能性就愈高。因此，內地供港食品高品質的根本原因，還在於『供給側』的自我要求」。<br />\n<br />\n根據國家質檢總局測算，今天香港市場九成活豬、活牛、蔬菜，以及三成活雞都從內地入口。文章強調，「事關港澳同胞的生命線安全，內地當然要高度重視」，又稱「內地供港澳食品維持高品質的秘密，藏在生產流程中，更藏在同胞真情裏」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180417/s00001/1523954255990\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180417%2Fs00001%2F1523954255990&d=%2BX6gucXTjJEYRhwp3Uk4ip4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=bc6eb41e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180417%2Fs00001%2F1523954255990&h=0f6367a7\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180417/s00001/1523954255990</a><br />\n<br />\n即係有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fd62e4f3421d20621a04b5a3e0af459b266ce61","tid":632413,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:11:12.000Z","msg":"係囉<br />\n<br />\n(毒米又入港)今次直接比山埃你食<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/575464/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/575464/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f9e6356055ce8d85f37c2377e95e6a6db134c55","tid":632413,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:12:16.000Z","msg":"係囉，係囉<br />\n<br />\n(毒米入港) 建議放寬米的鎘含量　政府稱考慮到市民飲食習慣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/519262/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/519262/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"3b09cf0bcf8b88a3637e4efad9bfd130677971de","tid":632413,"uid":119609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>古語有云「民以食為天」，食物安全一直備受關注。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d68872567b41081ac50adef015a6eaf5f9f166","tid":632413,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"係囉，係囉，係囉<br />\n<br />\n(共享榮耀)河源鎮政府強建垃圾場　東江水恐變垃圾水<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/114355/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/114355/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7f31dfc6ba0aaade92bb37c8d261e09e6205f362","tid":632413,"uid":62532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:19:34.000Z","msg":"咁點解供應其他地方既supplier自我要求咁低？<br />\n唔會係d農場祟&quot;港&quot;掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b32325586c1a28de9cef2ee78220408680e7155d","tid":632413,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:20:22.000Z","msg":"笑話"},{"pid":"5900560546c4ff1ec0f1c7fab012d80e949a31a7","tid":632413,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T12:52:24.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"a1909492d80cb4fd200ab0182a0e5c980c68b566","tid":632413,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"供垃圾劣貨過嚟有撚人買咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港又唔係無得揀，最多咪食外國冰鮮肉囉，係菜難避啲"},{"pid":"bfcde4116a11f05dba25e13939d75fffa03a2919","tid":632413,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f9e6356055ce8d85f37c2377e95e6a6db134c55","tid":632413,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:12:16.000Z","msg":"係囉，係囉<br />\n<br />\n(毒米入港) 建議放寬米的鎘含量　政府稱考慮到市民飲食習慣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/519262/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/519262/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"香港人唔食鎘唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a57742dd764dc9400c2d4f1e94ab319e89f0aeb","tid":632413,"uid":3331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a1909492d80cb4fd200ab0182a0e5c980c68b566","tid":632413,"uid":110019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T13:08:30.000Z","msg":"供垃圾劣貨過嚟有撚人買咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n香港又唔係無得揀，最多咪食外國冰鮮肉囉，係菜難避啲"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T17:10:47.000Z","msg":"已經預見倒香港政府會將個驗測外判<br />\n而中標既會係紅色企業<br />\n到時候合唔合格都只係一個字<br />\n就睇供應商識唔識做<br />\n如果你要外國既野食？<br />\n香港政府會直接同你講唔合格/唔適合香港人"},{"pid":"37a48621de01c5cf13b6173f284d69fe74f2c1cd","tid":632413,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T17:16:25.000Z","msg":"99.999%<br />\n香港七百萬人，即係每日有70人食咗屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b0e18155e6315bbfa487cb9e1efa57cda10fea3","tid":632413,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T18:55:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/30973\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F30973&d=%2BX6gucXTjJEYRhwp3Uk4ip4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=664c7677\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/30973</a><br />\n<br />\n2015年，香港從中國內地進口了99.5%（約158萬隻）活豬，剩下的0.5%來自台灣，本地豬場每天供應不足1%活豬。不過，香港人多數食的冰鮮及冷藏豬肉，大多來自巴西、德國、荷蘭、美國等地。把活豬（以每頭重110公斤計）、豬肉、豬內臟、火腿和五花腩等細項都加起來，中國供港豬肉只佔約44%供應。<br />\n<br />\n香港所有中國活牛均由內地進口，並由五豐行壟斷。把往年的新鮮牛肉的消耗量與活牛進口數目相除，再計算2015年進口活牛的重量，得出供港活牛只佔總進口量2%。如把所有牛肉製品（包括內臟、加工製品等）一併計算的話，牛肉主要從巴西和美國進口，中國的僅佔4%，與想像大相逕庭。"},{"pid":"14f085bc868531ef1789ef1537739c1b64aa1a60","tid":632413,"uid":81113,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bfcde4116a11f05dba25e13939d75fffa03a2919","tid":632413,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f9e6356055ce8d85f37c2377e95e6a6db134c55","tid":632413,"uid":81113,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T11:12:16.000Z","msg":"係囉，係囉<br />\n<br />\n(毒米入港) 建議放寬米的鎘含量　政府稱考慮到市民飲食習慣<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/519262/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/519262/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-17T13:13:18.000Z","msg":"香港人唔食鎘唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:27:03.000Z","msg":"食安中心d人收左幾多好處無人知"},{"pid":"5de00ba98d2523afffca42505d63658a5169a632","tid":632413,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T06:44:02.000Z","msg":"好少見 食安中同大陸鬥打飛機"},{"pid":"c0ebcb8c46362c962a4d4ebd931bfac017e857d7","tid":632413,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5de00ba98d2523afffca42505d63658a51